expression.expression-string: ' select * FROM (select distinct band_id FROM (SELECT * FROM event WHERE date >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL :event_date_start DAY) AND date <= DATE_ADD(CURDATE(), INTERVAL :event_date_end DAY)) ev INNER JOIN (SELECT distinct band_id, event_id FROM band_event) band_event on band_event.event_id = ev.id) band_performing INNER JOIN band b on band_performing.band_id = b.id'
